#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kshisen; is a solitaire-like game played using the standard set of Mahjong "
"tiles. Unlike Mahjong however, &kshisen; has only one layer of scrambled "
"tiles. You can remove matching pieces if they can be connected with a line "
"with at most two bends in it. At the same time, the line must not cross any "
"other tiles. To win a game of &kshisen; the player has to remove all the "
"tiles from the game board."
msgstr ""
"&kshisen; je igra, podobna pasjansi, ki se igra s standardnim nizom Mahjong "
"ploščic. Za razliko od Mahjonga pa &kshisen; ima samo eno plast premešanih "
"ploščic. Ujemajoče se dele lahko odstranite, če jih je mogoče povezati s "
"črto z največ dvema pregiboma. Hkrati črta ne sme prečkati drugih ploščic. "
"Za zmago v igri &kshisen; igralec mora odstraniti vse ploščice z igralne "
"plošče."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kshisen; gameboard"
msgstr "&kshisen; igralna plošča"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remove all the tiles from the game board within the shortest time possible."
msgstr "Odstranite vse ploščice z igralne plošče v najkrajšem možnem času."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kshisen; will load a default layout automatically once you start the game "
"and you can start playing right away."
msgstr ""
"&kshisen; bo samodejno naložil privzeto postavitev, ko začnete igro in lahko "
"začnete igrati takoj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should carefully study the tiles lied out on the game board and find two "
"tiles matching exactly. When you have found such a pair use your mouse to "
"select them."
msgstr ""
"Pozorno preučite ploščice na igralni plošči in poiščite dve ploščici, ki se "
"popolnoma ujemata. Ko najdete tak par, ju izberite z miško."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you select a matching pair of tiles they will vanish from the game "
"board. However, even if the tiles you select appear as open they will only "
"be removed from the board if they can be connected with a line having at "
"most two bends and not crossing any other tiles. Furthermore the line can "
"only be drawn horizontally and vertically."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete ujemajoči se par ploščic, bosta izginili z igralne plošče. Tudi "
"če so ploščice, ki jih izberete, prikazane kot odprte, bodo odstranjene s "
"plošče samo, če jih je mogoče povezati s črto, ki ima največ dva ovinka in "
"ne prečka nobene druge ploščice. Poleg tega je črto mogoče narisati samo "
"vodoravno in navpično."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Find as many matches as possible to remove all the tiles from the game board."
msgstr ""
"Poiščite čim več zadetkov, da odstranite vse ploščice z igralne plošče."

