#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Matching tiles are such tiles where the face pictograms match exactly."
msgstr ""
"Ujemajoče se ploščice so takšne ploščice, kjer se piktogrami obrazov "
"natančno ujemajo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:168 index.docbook:178 index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "Opomba:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are exceptions to this rule. In the traditional game of Mahjong each "
"tile has a matching one except for the <quote>Flowers</quote> and "
"<quote>Seasons</quote> tiles."
msgstr ""
"Obstajajo izjeme od tega pravila. V tradicionalni igri Mahjong ima vsaka "
"ploščica ujemajočo se ploščico, razen ploščic <quote>Rože</quote> in "
"<quote>Letni časi</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Flowers</quote> tiles have no doubles in the set and can be "
"matched directly to each other."
msgstr ""
"Ploščice <quote>Flowers</quote> v kompletu nimajo dvojnikov in jih je mogoče "
"povezati neposredno med seboj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Seasons</quote> tiles have no doubles in the set and can be "
"matched directly to each other."
msgstr ""
"Ploščice <quote>Letni časi</quote> v kompletu nimajo dvojnikov in jih je "
"mogoče povezati neposredno med seboj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tiles can only be removed if they can be connected with a maximum of three "
"connected lines that do not cross any other tile. Lines can be horizontal or "
"vertical, but not diagonal."
msgstr ""
"Ploščice je mogoče odstraniti samo, če jih je mogoče povezati z največ tremi "
"povezanimi črtami, ki ne sekajo nobene druge ploščice. Črte so lahko "
"vodoravne ali navpične, ne pa diagonalne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You do not have to draw the lines by yourself, the game does this for you. "
"Just mark two matching tiles on the board, if they can be connected by a "
"line with at most two bends, the line is drawn and the tiles are removed."
msgstr ""
"Ni vam treba risati črt sami, igra to naredi namesto vas. Samo označite dve "
"ujemajoči se ploščici na tabli, če ju lahko povežete s črto z največ dvema "
"pregiboma, črta se nariše in ploščice se odstranijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lines may only cross empty areas of the board."
msgstr "Črte lahko prečkajo le prazna področja plošče."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some games are unsolvable. If you would like to avoid unsolvable games check "
"the option <guilabel>Create solvable games only</guilabel> in the "
"configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere igre so nerešljive. Če se želite izogniti nerešljivim igram, "
"izberite možnost <guilabel>Ustvari samo rešljive igre</guilabel> v "
"konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The scores are awarded for the time the player needs to remove all the tiles "
"from the game board. Games with more tiles give more scores."
msgstr ""
"Rezultati se dodelijo za čas, ki ga igralec potrebuje, da odstrani vse "
"ploščice z igralne plošče. Igre z več ploščicami dajejo več točk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you played with the <guilabel>Gravity</guilabel> setting enabled, the "
"score will be doubled."
msgstr ""
"Če ste igrali z omogočeno nastavitvijo <guilabel>Težnost</guilabel>, bo "
"rezultat podvojen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To be eligible for a place amongst the high scores player has to complete a "
"game instance within the shortest period of time possible."
msgstr ""
"Da bi bil igralec upravičen do mesta med najboljšimi rezultati, mora "
"dokončati primer igre v najkrajšem možnem času."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the player uses the <quote>Undo</quote> or <quote>Hint</quote> feature "
"the record will not be considered as a high score."
msgstr ""
"Če igralec uporabi funkcijo <quote>Razveljavi</quote> ali <quote>Namig</"
"quote>, zapis ne bo obravnavan kot visok rezultat."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tips"
msgstr "Nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on a tile with the &RMB; to highlight all matching tiles on the board. "
"Unlike using the <quote>Undo</quote> or <quote>Hint</quote> feature, this "
"help is allowed without being considered cheating."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na ploščico z &RMB; da označite vse ujemajoče se ploščice na tabli. "
"Za razliko od uporabe funkcije <quote>Razveljavi</quote> ali <quote>Namig</"
"quote> je ta pomoč dovoljena, ne da bi se obravnavala kot goljufanje."

