#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change the way &kshisen; looks use the <link linkend=\"game-settings-"
"settings\">menubar</link> to open the <link linkend=\"configuration"
"\">configuration utility</link>."
msgstr ""
"Da. Če želite spremeniti način &kshisen; izgleda uporabite <link linkend="
"\"game-settings-settings\">menijsko vrstico</link>, da odprete <link linkend="
"\"configuration\">pripomoček za konfiguracijo</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use keyboard?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not feature a keyboard play mode."
msgstr "Ne. Ta igra nima načina igranja s tipkovnico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj moram zapustiti igro, vendar še nisem končal. Ali lahko shranim svoj "
"napredek?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not feature a <quote>Save</quote> option."
msgstr "Ne. Ta igra nima možnosti <quote>Shrani</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
"&kshisen;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item will open a configuration "
"dialog which lets you alter the behavior of the game."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kshisen;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, se "
"odpre konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno, ki vam omogoča spreminjanje obnašanja "
"igre."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kshisen; configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kshisen; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kshisen; configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kshisen; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>General</guilabel> page"
msgstr "Stran <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gravity"
msgstr "Težnost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking this makes the game even harder: If a tile is removed, all tiles "
"lying above it will fall down one step."
msgstr ""
"Če preverite to, je igra še težja: če ploščico odstranite, bodo vse "
"ploščice, ki ležijo nad njo, padle eno stopničko navzdol."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create solvable games only"
msgstr "Ustvari samo rešljive igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, you will only be presented with games that are possible to "
"solve. Note: Even in solvable games you can fail to complete if you remove "
"the tiles in the wrong order."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, vam bodo prikazane samo igre, ki jih je mogoče rešiti. "
"Opomba: Tudi v rešljivih igrah vam lahko ne uspe dokončati, če odstranite "
"ploščice v napačnem vrstnem redu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show message if board can no longer be solved"
msgstr "Pokaži sporočilo, če plošče ni več mogoče rešiti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, &kshisen; will try to analyze solvability of each game position "
"and show a message to abort the game in case there are no possible moves "
"left to win the game."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, &kshisen; bo poskušal analizirati rešljivost vsake igralne "
"pozicije in prikazal sporočilo za prekinitev igre, če ni več možnih potez za "
"zmago v igri."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use Chinese style: any flower match any flower, any season match any season"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite kitajski slog: katera koli roža se ujema z vsako rožo, kateri koli "
"letni čas se ujema z vsakim letnim časom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the traditional rules for matching the tiles. Previous version of "
"&kshisen; used to allow only exact tiles matches, which is inconsistent with "
"Mahjong rules. It is recommended to keep this option checked."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite tradicionalna pravila za ujemanje ploščic. Prejšnja različica "
"&kshisen; uporablja se za omogočanje samo natančnih ujemanj ploščic, kar ni "
"v skladu s pravili Mahjonga. Priporočljivo je, da to možnost obdržite "
"potrjeno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tiles can slide, but you can connect only in 2 lines instead of 3"
msgstr ""
"Ploščice lahko drsijo, vendar jih lahko povežete le v 2 vrsticah namesto v 3"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option changes the rules to the point where it almost becomes a "
"completely different game. When it is active, you can remove the tiles only "
"if they can be connected by a line consisting of one or two segments instead "
"of the customary three. However, you are allowed to slide the tiles on the "
"board, if the row or column where they are placed has some empty space. To "
"make a sliding move, you have to click first on the tile in the column or "
"row that can slide, and then on the matching tile. If there are two possible "
"sliding moves, blue lines are shown indicating these moves. You then have to "
"click on one of the two lines to choose your preferred move."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost spremeni pravila do te mere, da skoraj postane popolnoma drugačna "
"igra. Ko je aktiven, lahko ploščice odstranite le, če jih je mogoče povezati "
"s črto, sestavljeno iz enega ali dveh segmentov namesto običajnih treh. "
"Vendar pa lahko ploščice drsite po tabli, če je v vrstici ali stolpcu, kjer "
"so postavljene, nekaj praznega prostora. Če želite izvesti drsečo potezo, "
"morate najprej klikniti ploščico v stolpcu ali vrstici, ki lahko drsi, nato "
"pa še ujemajočo se ploščico. Če sta možni dve drseči potezi, so prikazane "
"modre črte, ki označujejo te poteze. Nato morate klikniti eno od dveh "
"vrstic, da izberete želeno potezo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid "Board Difficulty"
msgstr "Težavnost deske"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The slider controls the difficulty of the board (&ie; how much the tiles are "
"shuffled) from <guilabel>Easy</guilabel> to <guilabel>Hard</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Drsnik nadzira težavnost plošče (tj. koliko so ploščice premešane) od "
"<guilabel>Enostavno</guilabel> do <guilabel>Težko</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "Piece Removal Speed"
msgstr "Hitrost odstranjevanja kosov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adjusting this slider alters the speed at which the pieces are removed from "
"the screen after a match has been made."
msgstr ""
"Prilagoditev tega drsnika spremeni hitrost, s katero se figure po ujemanju "
"odstranijo z zaslona."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "Board Size"
msgstr "Velikost plošče"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This slider allows you to change the number of tiles on the board. The more "
"tiles you have, the harder (and longer) the game will be."
msgstr ""
"Ta drsnik vam omogoča spreminjanje števila ploščic na plošči. Več ploščic "
"kot imate, težja (in daljša) bo igra."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Tiles</guilabel> and <guilabel>Background</guilabel> page"
msgstr "<guilabel>Ploščice</guilabel> in stran <guilabel>Ozadje</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select you favorite design for tiles and background."
msgstr "Izberite svoj najljubši dizajn za ploščice in ozadje."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens &kshisen; help pages (this document)."
msgstr "Odpre &kshisen; strani s pomočjo (ta dokument)."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>OK</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>V redu</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves your changes and closes the dialog."
msgstr "Shrani vaše spremembe in zapre pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "Apply"
msgstr "Uveljavi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves your changes but does not close the dialog."
msgstr "Shrani vaše spremembe, vendar ne zapre pogovornega okna."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Prekliči"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid "Discards all your changes and closes the dialog."
msgstr "Zavrže vse vaše spremembe in zapre pogovorno okno."

